'''Leopards''' ({{Vol-la|Panthera pardus}} (Linnaeus, 1758), {{Vol-en|leopard}}, {{Vol-ru|леопард}}, {{Vol-lv|leopards}}) irā leļs [[Kaču saime|kaču saimis]] (''Felidae'') plieseigais [[zviers]]. Leopards dzeivoj Afrikā i Azejas dinavidos<ref name="ADV">[http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/site/accounts/information/Panthera_pardus.html University of Michigan Museum of Zoology]</ref>.

